<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>CareerTrack | Track. Apply. Succeed.</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/responsive.css" />
</head>
<body>

<%- include("partials/public-navbar") %>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-content">
      <p class="tagline">Track. Apply. Succeed.</p>
      <h1>Manage Every Job Application in One Smart Dashboard</h1>
      <p class="hero-text">
        CareerTrack helps students and job seekers track applications, interviews,
        offers, rejections, reminders, and progress — all in one place.
      </p>

      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="/register" class="primary-btn">Start Tracking</a>
        <a href="/dashboard" class="secondary-btn">View Demo</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-card">
      <h3>Application Overview</h3>

      <div class="stats-grid">
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h2>24</h2>
          <p>Total Applied</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h2>8</h2>
          <p>Interviews</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h2>3</h2>
          <p>Offers</p>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-card">
          <h2>5</h2>
          <p>Rejected</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="progress-box">
        <p>Monthly Progress</p>
        <div class="progress-bar">
          <span></span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features" id="features">
    <div class="section-title">
      <p>Powerful Features</p>
      <h2>Everything You Need to Stay Organized</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="features-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📌 Application Tracking</h3>
        <p>Add, update, delete and manage all your job and internship applications.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📅 Interview Reminders</h3>
        <p>Never miss an interview with reminders and notification support.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📊 Dashboard Analytics</h3>
        <p>Track applied, shortlisted, selected and rejected applications visually.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>🔐 Secure Login</h3>
        <p>User authentication with protected personal application data.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>🔎 Search & Filter</h3>
        <p>Quickly find applications based on company, role, status or date.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="feature-card">
        <h3>📩 Email Alerts</h3>
        <p>Get useful alerts for interview dates and important application updates.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <section class="audience">
  <div class="section-title">
    <p>Who Can Use CareerTrack?</p>
    <h2>Built for Students, Freshers and Job Seekers</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>🎓 Students</h3>
      <p>Track internships, campus placements, training programs and application deadlines.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>💼 Freshers</h3>
      <p>Manage multiple job applications, interviews and company responses in one dashboard.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <h3>🚀 Career Switchers</h3>
      <p>Organize job search progress, notes, reminders and follow-up actions professionally.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="preview-section">
  <div class="preview-content">
    <p class="tagline">Dashboard Preview</p>
    <h2>Visualize Your Career Progress</h2>
    <p>
      CareerTrack gives you a clean overview of your total applications,
      interviews, selected opportunities, rejected applications and upcoming tasks.
    </p>

    <ul class="preview-list">
      <li>✅ Application status summary</li>
      <li>✅ Upcoming interview reminders</li>
      <li>✅ Recent application history</li>
      <li>✅ Analytics for better decisions</li>
    </ul>

    <a href="/dashboard" class="primary-btn">Explore Dashboard</a>
  </div>

  <div class="dashboard-preview">
    <div class="preview-top">
      <h3>Career Dashboard</h3>
      <span>Live Preview</span>
    </div>

    <div class="mini-bars">
      <div><span style="width: 85%;"></span></div>
      <div><span style="width: 65%;"></span></div>
      <div><span style="width: 45%;"></span></div>
      <div><span style="width: 75%;"></span></div>
    </div>

    <div class="preview-table">
      <p><strong>Accenture</strong> <span>Interview</span></p>
      <p><strong>TCS</strong> <span>Applied</span></p>
      <p><strong>Infosys</strong> <span>Selected</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="why-choose">
  <div class="section-title">
    <p>Why Choose Us?</p>
    <h2>More Than a Simple Tracker</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <span>01</span>
      <h3>Organized Workflow</h3>
      <p>No more scattered notes, screenshots or forgotten applications.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <span>02</span>
      <h3>Smart Reminders</h3>
      <p>Stay prepared for interviews, follow-ups and important career deadlines.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <span>03</span>
      <h3>Secure Dashboard</h3>
      <p>Your application data stays connected with your personal account.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="testimonials">
  <div class="section-title">
    <p>User Feedback</p>
    <h2>What Users Say</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="features-grid">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <p>“CareerTrack helped me manage all my internship applications without confusion.”</p>
      <h3>- MCA Student</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <p>“The dashboard makes it easy to know where I stand in my job search.”</p>
      <h3>- Fresher</h3>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <p>“A simple but useful platform for tracking interviews and offers.”</p>
      <h3>- Job Seeker</h3>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="faq">
  <div class="section-title">
    <p>FAQ</p>
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
  </div>

  <div class="faq-container">
    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Is CareerTrack free?</h3>
      <p>Yes, CareerTrack is designed as a free platform for students and job seekers.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Can I track internships also?</h3>
      <p>Yes, you can track both job and internship applications.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item">
      <h3>Will it support reminders?</h3>
      <p>Yes, interview and follow-up reminder features will be added with backend integration.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  </section>
  <section class="how-it-works">
    <div class="section-title">
      <p>Simple Process</p>
      <h2>How CareerTrack Works</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <span>01</span>
        <h3>Create Account</h3>
        <p>Register and login securely to access your personal dashboard.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <span>02</span>
        <h3>Add Applications</h3>
        <p>Enter company name, role, status, interview date and notes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="step">
        <span>03</span>
        <h3>Track Progress</h3>
        <p>Monitor application status, interviews, offers and reports.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta">
    <h2>Ready to Organize Your Career Journey?</h2>
    <p>Start tracking your job and internship applications professionally.</p>
    <a href="/register" class="primary-btn">Create Free Account</a>
  </section>

  <%- include("partials/footer") %>

  <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
</body>
</html>